OL,6,FOfcom has given more details of its   
OL,7,Freview of the rules covering          
OL,8,Fadvertising on ITV, Channel 4 and     
OL,9,FChannel 5.                            
OL,11,FIt is seeking views on whether        
OL,12,Fadditional rules still need to apply to
OL,13,Fthese three channels.                 
OL,15,FThere are three particular rules which
OL,16,Fmay change:                           
OL,18,FCrucially there is no suggestion of   
OL,19,Frelaxing the rule which means there can
OL,20,Fbe no more than 12 minutes of adverts 
OL,21,Fin any "clock hour".                  
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
