OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1662211378
OL,6,FThe clarification from Ofcom about the
OL,7,Fdetails of their review is helpful and
OL,8,Fmakes it easier to look at how the    
OL,9,Fviewing experience could change in    
OL,10,Fpractice.                             
OL,12,FIn a couple of earlier articles, I    
OL,13,Fnoted how ITV already runs 12 minutes 
OL,14,Fan hour of adverts during many of its 
OL,15,Fmost popular and lucrative programmes 
OL,16,Fespecially between 4pm and 6pm and    
OL,17,Fbetween 7pm and the start of News at  
OL,18,FTen.                                  
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
OL,22,                                   G2/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
