SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1662211378
OL,6,FOn a typical day, there is at least 10
OL,7,Fminutes 30 seconds of advertising in  
OL,8,Fevery clock hour except those beginning
OL,9,Fat 6am, 2pm, 3pm, 6pm, 10pm and 11pm. 
OL,10,FThere is, of course, little or no     
OL,11,Fadvertising after midnight.           
OL,13,FThe only dramatic changes would be in 
OL,14,Fthe two "news hours" although a few   
OL,15,Fprogramme durations may have to be    
OL,16,Freduced slightly to make the schedule 
OL,17,Ffit together properly.                
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
OL,22,                                   G3/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
