PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1662211378
OL,6,FBut one crucial question is whether too
OL,7,Fmuch advertising could simply be      
OL,8,Fcounterproductive and scare viewers   
OL,9,Foff.                                  
OL,11,FWhen hour long dramas started to have 
OL,12,Fthree internal breaks rather than two 
OL,13,Faround 20 years ago, there was some   
OL,14,Finitial backlash.                     
OL,16,FLooking at the potential changes, there
OL,17,Fcould be a trade off between longer   
OL,18,Fbreaks and more frequent breaks.      
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
OL,22,                                   G4/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35605
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1662211378
OL,6,FITV could, in theory, schedule two    
OL,7,Fbreaks during Emmerdale if the rules  
OL,8,Fwere relaxed. But they would be very  
OL,9,Fbrave to do this  especially when, in
OL,10,Fpractice, that would not allow them to
OL,11,Fshow any more advertising during that 
OL,12,Fhour.                                 
OL,14,FOn the other hand, could the option of
OL,15,Frunning internal breaks of a longer   
OL,16,Fduration prove handy? This can already
OL,17,Fhappen during films to reduce the     
OL,18,Fnumber of breaks.                     
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
