OL,6,FAt present, there are three breaks of 
OL,7,F3.30 during the first hour of This    
OL,8,FMorning. Would it be less disruptive to
OL,9,Fextend these breaks to 4 minutes'     
OL,10,Fduration rather than add in an extra 90
OL,11,Fsecond break?                         
OL,13,FOfcom will seek views over the next few
OL,14,Fmonths then spell out what changes, if
OL,15,Fany, it proposes.                     
OL,17,FBut there is one other suggestion from
OL,18,FOfcom which is potentially concerning.
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
OL,4,Cproposed ad changes for PSBs          
