OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1662211378
OL,6,FIt is also seeking views on whether the
OL,7,Frule which prevents ITV, Channel 4 and
OL,8,FChannel 5 running teleshopping before 
OL,9,Fmidnight should go. To my mind, this  
OL,10,Fwould undoubtedly be a damaging       
OL,11,Fdevelopment and should be resisted.   
OL,13,FUltimately though it is becoming      
OL,14,Fincreasingly hard to justify actual   
OL,15,Frestrictions on the three channels    
OL,16,Fwhich do not apply to others. The     
OL,17,Fimportant thing is to hold them to    
OL,18,Fpositive requirements and help make   
OL,19,Fthese requirements viable.            
OL,3,COfcom provides further information on 
